data.description: Highly desired South Knoxville Community and school system with an easy walk to schools and the Greenway in your backyard. Elegant, updated, open-concept home has custom features throughout. This updated and vibey rancher with split bedroom and open floor plan features an oversized en suite with spa tub and stand up shower, water closet and BIG walk in closet! Feature walls and natural light from large windows throughout the home. All white kitchen with walk in pantry, gas fire place, flat fenced yard and back deck to enjoy! This home is the first house on the right in the neighborhood with an extended driveway for additional parking!
